Select One - User Group Custom Field
The details of the members of a group stored within a 
Select One - User Group
 custom field can be referenced using the following syntax:

[#(?object=group::id=@
fieldname
@) ... #]
Where:

fieldname
 is the name of the 
Select One - User Group
 field.
 Replace "..." with the contact 
variables
 you wish to display. 
i.e. ~lastname~
The role the user is assigned within the group can be accessed using 
~role~
 in the above syntax.
